# Day 8: Seven Segment Search

## Setup

```elixir
Mix.install([
  {:kino, "~> 0.4.1"}
])
```

## Input

```elixir
input = Kino.Input.textarea("Input")
```

## Part 1

```elixir
Kino.Input.read(input)
|> String.split("\n", trim: true)
|> Enum.map(fn line ->
  line
  |> String.split("|")
  |> List.to_tuple()
  |> elem(1)
  |> String.split(" ", trim: true)
  |> Enum.map(&String.length(&1))
  |> Enum.filter(&Enum.member?([2, 4, 3, 7], &1))
  |> Enum.count()
end)
|> Enum.sum()
```
